import React from 'react'
import {
	SidebarContainer,
	Icon,
	CloseIcon,
} from './SidebarElements'

const Sidebar = () => {
	return (
		<SidebarContainer>
			<Icon>
				<CloseIcon />
			</Icon>
			<SidebarWrapper>
				<SidebarMenu>
					<SidebarLink to="about">
						About
					</SidebarLink>
					<SidebarLink to="discover">
						Discover
					</SidebarLink>
					<SidebarLink to="services">
						Services
					</SidebarLink>
					<SidebarLink to="signup">
						Sign Up
					</SidebarLink>
				</SidebarMenu>
				<SideBtnWrap>
					<SidebarRoute to='/signin'>Sign In</SidebarRoute>
				</SideBtnWrap>
			</SidebarWrapper>
		</SidebarContainer>
	)
}

export default Sidebar
